  "subject": "Refactored Dsl parser",
  "commit_message": "Refactored Dsl parser\n\nsupports all characters except newlines for queries\nsupports escaped single quotes in queries\nseparated lexer and parser in antlr grammar\nreduced complexity of DslListener by modifying parser\nremoved DslContext because it was no longer needed after parser updates\nadded additional unit tests for new features\nadded parser and lexer error listeners\nDslQueryBuilder no longer uses Antlr objects\nDslQueryBuilder is now stateless\n\nChange-Id: Ia8580a1a53259fd69128b3a83c0c8fc743672fa7\nIssue-ID: AAI-2225\nSigned-off-by: Benjamin, Max (mb388a) <mb388a@us.att.com>\n",
